parameters: "..I said I didn't want to.. but.. that person.."

No matter how many times Hinori spoke to her, she only muttered with empty
eyes.

"You guys.. are guests? You seem lost. If you leave here and turn left at
the end of the hallway, there's a ventilation duct. Hurry and escape."

"You're telling us to escape.. but you shouldn't be worrying about us. Come
with us too.."

"Do you worry about us? You haven't been taken in by the village yet. But..
it's better to get rid of those kinds of emotions early. It's very
dangerous to stay normal in this village. We will eventually finish our
punishment and leave here, but you boys.."
"..It's nothing. Now go quickly. You must never come back here again."
"Come on, hurry up and go. You can never come back here again."
(That guy is still nearby.. Let's wait until he passes by.)

(That's the room the person from earlier went into.. Let's not go in
there.)
